Chuck Taylor All Star Low GS 'Tie Dye - Spring Pink'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Low GS Tie Dye ‘Spring Pink’ showcases a psychedelic print throughout the upper, constructed from 12oz canvas and lined in breathable mesh. Traditional Converse All Star branding lands on the woven tongue tag and the license plate that decorates the white rubber midsole. A matching white finish is applied to the outsole, featuring a customary diamond traction pattern for optimal grip.

Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Allover Metallic Stars - White'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘Allover Metallic Stars’ updates the vintage high-top with an archival star print fashioned for big kids. Crisp white canvas is utilized on the upper, covered in orderly rows of metallic stars in a full spectrum of colors. The sneaker sits on a white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes and a standard Converse All Star license plate. Midfoot eyelets offer enhanced breathability, while a SmartFOAM sockliner delivers a cushioned ride.

Chuck Taylor All Star Superplay Sandal GS 'Unicorns'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Superplay Sandal GS ‘Unicorns’ combines the open breathability of a sandal with the lightweight cushioning of a sneaker. Adjustable straps secure the synthetic leather upper, covered in a playful unicorn print and lined in soft textile. A webbing strap atop the tongue provides easy on and off, while a reinforced toe cap offers improved durability. The slip-on is mounted on a solid white EVA midsole for a smooth ride.

Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Sunflowers - Pink'
results.story: Offered in big kid sizing, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘Sunflowers’ enlivens the classic high-top with a sunny, playful aesthetic. The pink canvas upper displays a cheerful sunflower print on each side panel, depicting blossoms that appear to sprout up from the white rubber midsole. A SmartFOAM sockliner delivers enhanced comfort, while the brown rubber outsole features a traditional diamond tread for reliable traction.

Dunk Low PS 'Michigan' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Michigan’ brings back an OG colorway in little kids sizing. Rendered in low-top form, the retro hoops shoe features a simple two-tone design that pays homage to the Michigan Wolverines — one of the universities included in 1985’s classic ‘Be True to Your School’ pack. An all-leather upper in Varsity Maize and Midnight Navy sits atop a contrasting white midsole. Standard Nike branding decorates the woven tongue tag and heel tab.

Air More Uptempo PS 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Nike Air More Uptempo PS ‘White Varsity Red’ revives a 2005 release in little kids sizing. The elemental two-tone colorway, alternately known as the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ displays prominent ‘Air’ branding across the white leather upper, with each oversized letter outlined in red. A lightweight foam midsole is enhanced with visible Nike Air cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Air More Uptempo GS 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air More Uptempo GS ‘White Varsity Red’ brings back a simplistic 2005 colorway in big kids sizing. Alternately dubbed the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ the vintage hoops shoe features a perforated white leather upper with oversized ‘Air’ lettering outlined in red. Retro details include dual pull loops, a jewel Swoosh at the heel and a speed lacing system augmented by elastic straps. The mid-top sits on a full-length Phylon midsole with a visible Air sole unit under the heel.

Air Max 90 PS 'Evolution of Icons'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Air Max 90 PS ‘Evolution of Icons’ celebrates the history of Air with a variety of vintage logos printed on the sockliner. The exterior build comprises a breathable white mesh base with grey suede overlays and a matching leather mudguard. Vibrant accents give a further nod to Air Max history, highlighted by Volt-colored eyelets, a turquoise Swoosh and Infrared cassette detailing around the visible Max Air unit. An added pink mini-Swoosh decorates the lateral forefoot.
